---
import MainLayout from '../layouts/MainLayout.astro';

const lastUpdated = 'Oktoba 23, 2025';
---

<MainLayout
  title="Manufar Sirri - Technologiya"
  description="Koyi yadda muke kiyaye bayananku da tsaron ku a Technologiya"
>
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 py-12">
    
    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center mb-16">
      <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-blue-600 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6">
        <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z"></path>
        </svg>
      </div>
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100 mb-4">
        Manufar Sirri
      </h1>
      <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">
        An sabunta: {lastUpdated}
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Key Points -->
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mb-16">
      <div class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-xl p-6 shadow-lg text-center">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-green-100 dark:bg-green-900/30 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-green-600 dark:text-green-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 15v2m-6 4h12a2 2 0 002-2v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2zm10-10V7a4 4 0 00-8 0v4h8z"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100 mb-2">
          Tsaro Mai Ƙarfi
        </h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">
          Bayananku suna cikin aminci tare da ɓoyewa mai ƙarfi
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-xl p-6 shadow-lg text-center">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-blue-100 dark:bg-blue-900/30 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 12a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z"></path>
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M2.458 12C3.732 7.943 7.523 5 12 5c4.478 0 8.268 2.943 9.542 7-1.274 4.057-5.064 7-9.542 7-4.477 0-8.268-2.943-9.542-7z"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100 mb-2">
          Bayani Mai Haske
        </h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">
          Muna bayyana yadda muke amfani da bayananku
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-xl p-6 shadow-lg text-center">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-purple-100 dark:bg-purple-900/30 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-purple-600 dark:text-purple-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4 7v10c0 2.21 3.582 4 8 4s8-1.79 8-4V7M4 7c0 2.21 3.582 4 8 4s8-1.79 8-4M4 7c0-2.21 3.582-4 8-4s8 1.79 8 4"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100 mb-2">
          Ikon Ku
        </h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">
          Kuna da cikakken iko kan bayananku
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Main Content -->
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <div class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-xl p-8 md:p-12 shadow-lg space-y-8">
        
        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100 mb-4">
            1. Gabatarwa
          </h2>
          <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mb-4">
            Technologiya ("mu", "namu", ko "shafin") yana jaddada kiyaye sirrin masu amfani da mu. Wannan manufar sirri ta bayyana yadda muke tattara, amfani, da kare bayananku lokacin da kuke amfani da shafin mu.
          </p>
          <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
            Ta amfani da shafin mu, kuna yarda da tattara da amfani da bayanai kamar yadda aka bayyana a wannan manufa.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100 mb-4">
            2. Bayanan da Muke Tattarawa
          </h2>
          
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100 mb-3 mt-4">
            2.1 Bayanai da Kuke Bayarwa
          </h3>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 ml-4">
            <li>Suna da adireshin email lokacin yin rajista</li>
            <li>Bayanin martaba (idan akwai)</li>
            <li>Sharhi da maganganun da kuke aikawa</li>
            <li>Saƙonnin tuntuɓar mu</li>
          </ul>

          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100 mb-3 mt-4">
            2.2 Bayanan da Ake Tattarawa Ta Atomatik
          </h3>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 ml-4">
            <li>Adireshin IP</li>
            <li>Nau'in burauzar da na'urar da kuke amfani</li>
            <li>Lokacin da zarar ku wannan shafin</li>
            <li>Shafukan da kuka ziyarta</li>
            <li>Cookies da fasahar kamancin haka</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100 mb-4">
            3. Yadda Muke Amfani da Bayananku
          </h2>
          <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mb-4">
            Muna amfani da bayanan da muka tattara don:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 ml-4">
            <li>Samar da kuma inganta hidimominmu</li>
            <li>Gina asusunku da kula da shi</li>
            <li>Aika muku da labarai da sabuntawa (idan kun yarda)</li>
            <li>Amsa tambayoyin ku da kuma tallafa muku</li>
            <li>Kare shafin daga yaudara da cin zarafi</li>
            <li>Duba yadda ake amfani da shafin mu don ingantawa</li>
            <li>Bin dokokin da ƙa'idodi</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100 mb-4">
            4. Raba Bayanai
          </h2>
          <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mb-4">
            Ba ma sayar da bayananku ga wani. Muna iya raba bayananku da:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 ml-4">
            <li><strong>Masu samar da sabis:</strong> Kamfanonin da suke taimaka mana gudanar da shafin (misali, hosting, analytics)</li>
            <li><strong>Doka:</strong> Idan doka ta buƙata ko don kare haƙƙoƙinmu</li>
            <li><strong>Canje-canje na kasuwanci:</strong> Idan muka haɗa ko mu sayar da shafin</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100 mb-4">
            5. Cookies
          </h2>
          <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mb-4">
            Muna amfani da cookies da fasahar kamancin haka don:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 ml-4">
            <li>Tunawa da zaɓuɓɓukanku (misali, yaren da ka'idan duhu/haske)</li>
            <li>Gane idan kun shiga</li>
            <li>Duba yadda ake amfani da shafin</li>
            <li>Inganta ƙwarewar mai amfani</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mt-4">
            Kuna iya hana cookies ta saitunan burauzarku, amma wannan na iya taƙaita wasu ayyuka na shafin.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100 mb-4">
            6. Tsaron Bayanai
          </h2>
          <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
            Muna ɗaukar matakan tsaro mai ƙarfi don kare bayananku, ciki har da:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 ml-4 mt-4">
            <li>Ɓoyewa (encryption) na bayanai</li>
            <li>Sabar SSL/TLS don sadarwa mai tsaro</li>
            <li>Iyakance samun dama ga bayanan sirri</li>
            <li>Binciken tsaro na yau da kullum</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mt-4">
            Ko da yake muna ƙoƙari, babu tsarin tsaro da ke 100% mai aminci. Ba za mu iya ba da tabbaci cikakke ba.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100 mb-4">
            7. Haƙƙoƙinku
          </h2>
          <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mb-4">
            Kuna da haƙƙin:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 ml-4">
            <li><strong>Samun dama:</strong> Neman kwafin bayananku</li>
            <li><strong>Gyarawa:</strong> Gyara bayanan da ba daidai ba</li>
            <li><strong>Gogewa:</strong> Neman share bayananku</li>
            <li><strong>Ƙin yarda:</strong> Ƙin amfani da bayananku</li>
            <li><strong>Canja wurin bayanai:</strong> Neman canja bayananku zuwa wani sabis</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mt-4">
            Don amfani da waɗannan haƙƙoƙi, tuntuɓe mu a info@technologiya.com
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100 mb-4">
            8. Yara
          </h2>
          <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
            Shafin mu ba don yara 'yan ƙasa da shekaru 13 ba ne. Ba ma tattara bayanan yara da gangan. Idan kun gane cewa yaro ya bayar da bayanai, tuntuɓe mu nan da nan don mu share su.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100 mb-4">
            9. Haɗin Wasu Shafuka
          </h2>
          <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
            Shafin mu na iya ƙunsar haɗin zuwa wasu shafuka. Ba mu da iko kan manufofin sirri na waɗannan shafuka. Muna ba da shawarar ku karanta manufofinsu lokacin da kuka ziyarce su.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100 mb-4">
            10. Canje-canje ga Wannan Manufa
          </h2>
          <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
            Muna iya sabunta wannan manufa lokaci-lokaci. Za mu sanar da ku ta hanyar sanya sabon kwanan sabuntawa a saman shafin. Muna ba da shawarar ku duba manufan akai-akai.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100 mb-4">
            11. Tuntuɓe Mu
          </h2>
          <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mb-4">
            Idan kuna da tambayoyi ko damuwa game da wannan manufar sirri, tuntuɓe mu:
          </p>
          <div class="bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-900 rounded-lg p-6">
            <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">
              <li><strong>Email:</strong> info@technologiya.com</li>
              <li><strong>Waya:</strong> +234 800 000 0000</li>
              <li><strong>Adireshi:</strong> Kano, Najeriya</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </section>

      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Bottom CTA -->
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto mt-12">
      <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-600 to-blue-800 rounded-xl p-8 text-center text-white">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">
          Akwai Tambayoyi?
        </h2>
        <p class="text-lg mb-6 opacity-90">
          Idan kuna da wata tambaya game da manufar sirri, ba ku da damuwa tuntuɓe mu
        </p>
        <a
          href="/contact"
          class="inline-block px-6 py-3 bg-white text-blue-600 font-semibold rounded-lg hover:bg-gray-100 transition-colors"
        >
          Tuntuɓe Mu
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</MainLayout>
